subject: Basketball
College Athletics
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Kia Vaughn scored 12 of her 16 points in the final 10 minutes and host Rutgers closed with a 25-4 spurt in a 63-39 victory against No. 22 Pittsburgh on Saturday.
